    <h1 id=title>Maria Leopoldina of Austria</h1>
    <h2>The woman responsible for Brazil's independence as a country.<h2>
      <div id=img-div>
        <img id=image src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-bzgImrXvomU/VfYkQqMEfXI/AAAAAAAA5Yg/FBJa3LzHjR8/s1600/4.jpg">
